            "desc": "Mint a consent ASA and store the ZK-committed record in box storage.\ncommitment = Poseidon(data_type_hash, purpose_hash, salt) \u2014 data never touches the chain in plaintext. nullifier = SHA256(identity_secret || consent_id) \u2014 anti-replay.\nReturns the newly created asset ID.",
